        </mxCell>

        <!-- caption -->
        <mxCell id="cap" value="Figure 6. Observability topology. Each service exposes a Prometheus simpleclient endpoint on its own port; Prometheus scrapes all three at 5-second intervals. The metric names listed are those used in the SLOs reported in §6 (throughput, deduplication accuracy, P99 join latency)." style="text;html=1;align=center;fontSize=10;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1">
